Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:01:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Note: Style was set to "*Default" for every line. I hat to change it to "Default" for TPP to work. Don't know it that's relevant. -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, practice using the mouthpiece only.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dissatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just that... I really want to play as well as Rio-senpai as soon as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very Spartan, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I look forward to learning from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go eat breakfast first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dining hall is over there. I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rough and ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best from today onwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:01.97,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,92)}First Battle{Edit to match final of ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:01.97,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,414)}The Story of a Chair{Edit to match final of ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this was originally prepared to welcome you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we put our hearts into making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very thankful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring in everything that was being dried up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to sleep, at least do it after you eat. {Niphty: Split this from above line to read better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving it... my all... {Captain!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying...{Niphty: Barely audible, but it sounds like she's saying ganbatte here. Maybe find a better way to state this in editing, to make all these lines flow well in an English convo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up. The food is getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, allow me to properly introduce the members of 1121st Platoon. {Platoon 1121, or 1121st Platoon, what was the decision here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First is our Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Filicia Heideman. I'm a tank commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noël...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagi... Noël.{Yeah... I'm preserving spoken order here. Heck, everyone but Felicia is using Eastern order >_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporal Kannagi. She's a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's also a mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the last one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Second Class Suminoya Kureha. I'm a gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm younger than you, I came here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should listen to every—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran out of strength, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work, Noël-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's eat.{pls 2 mail some to me, it's 4 in the morning and I'm hungry}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I personally made the bacon. Give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a soldier and playing the bugle requires a strong body.{STAMINA??}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So eat up and grow stronger! {don't forget she needs to hit puberty first}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.{there are those push up bras you could, you know?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we're done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...show her around the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually very busy, but I don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this was an order, I {\i1}have{\i0} to show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y–Yes! I hope we can work well together, Kureha-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so informal with me, Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Private Suminoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, face the national and platoon flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 1121st Platoon currently only has five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 2nd Lieutenant, a Sergeant Major, a Corporal, and two Privates. {Capping them made them stand out better on the line.. remove if you dislike.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, five in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the smallest size a platoon can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're all elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our platoon is equipped with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One tank, one heavy machine gun, two light machine guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,four rifles, and five handguns...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using these weapons, our mission is to ensure that the region around the Seize border remains safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Private Suminoya! I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. You are permitted to speak, Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, beyond Seize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that the area beyond is Nomansland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is where the border of Helvetia extends to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the national border! The front lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very important base!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot fail to keep our vigil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At night, it'll be divided up between the five of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only for two years, so cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only hotline in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a call comes, it must be something serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, everyone will be woken up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll immediately be placed on Level-One Alert status.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second floor is the Commander's quarters as well as the battle strategy room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal conditions, entry is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...freely permitted for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But be sure to knock first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boiling water and cleaning are a part of regular duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathing is done in order of rank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's more enjoyable to bathe together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it Noël-chan's turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she seemed pretty worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, you're setting a bad example for the new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it when we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Commander should act like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take a {\i1}good{\i0} look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main tank that the 1121st Platoon is equipped with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector 0-Series Automated Walker Tank, Takemikazuchi.{To editor: - can be removed if it seems better; The tank type can mean automated walker tank, etc. Feel free to discuss with Niphty to find a better solution}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much larger than what we trained with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the zero-generation tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are less than ten of these antediluvian relics left in the nation.{N: leaving Antediluvian for epicness}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are amazing tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But its legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are still under repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just don't have enough parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, we don't have any manuals either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we can't even find the parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël will think of something, so it's not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you dare call it an accessory!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure... some day... for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we're laid back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really are quite leisurely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People say we're the Burden Platoon of Seize — that we're just a formality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're a pink squad, we don't even have a single functioning tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tour is now over! Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they're getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is a little troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, after you sent Kana-chan to bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! Why is she our communications person?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we say that new members would be ammunition-loaders or pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Command sent her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you want and what you get are often different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio will surely still adore you, just like she always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the way she acts, she's a really bright child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she's noticed something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous. Weren't you just half-asleep, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it too — the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near the barracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you agreeing with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that normal? Having ghosts—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, stop talking already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a technician, you should have done some proper scientific investigation before reporting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! Ghosts don't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. No way. No way! They definitely don't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Ghosts don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They definitely aren't real!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most certainly not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go conduct a proper investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you encounter something, just blow your bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send reinforcements immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Private...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kana... Private!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels... very exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunder sounds like a marching song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission! Not play time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it Kana... Private Sorami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take the point. I'll back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has been this way even before the fort was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.84,XMtS says hi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz345\pos(443.875,265.333333)}Modern Lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideograms. I wonder what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't read it, don't sit there fixated on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if we could read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just useless junk from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... aren't ghosts here to protect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we celebrated ghosts at the village where I was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and held a festival every year to show our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of village are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These so-called ghosts possess people,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drink their blood, and control dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are {\i1}very{\i0} devious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats usually carry lots of deadly diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Private Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just what I think, but could this place possibly have been a school before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Even the capital doesn't have a school this large.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But weren't there more people a long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this place must have been filled with lots of kids like us back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they all studied together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must have been where they taught music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside of the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read this, but...{N - she says "characters" but it doesn't sound right}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-sharp.{d sharp my ass, it's out of tune like hell, might've even been an G before. CM: That note was painful...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds... never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you just standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha-chan! Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Seize. The buildings inside the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in our platoon. Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a small useless unit stationed way out in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:19:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our tank doesn't even work, and they forget to send supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missions have always been just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're really laid back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you love it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this wonderful 1121st Platoon that I'm a part of and love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the gunner, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is our ghost... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this looks like a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure look like the thief from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you... I'm going to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't scare wounded animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking that it probably has nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, remember what our platoon's emblem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you roast it, it'll be bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even gave it a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost died yesterday because of this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also the reason that I got to go on a great adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:21:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? That wasn't fit to be called an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. I guess we'll decide by voting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. By Commander's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But next time you steal food, you'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was Rio this morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kanata did it every day, we'd start getting complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find the exact same chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it especially for you or anything.{tsundere, what}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.45,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous. Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food...
