Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:13.33,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kono sora no kagayaki kimi no mune ni todoiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:13.33,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The luminance of the sky has reached your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:23.36,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}yumemiteta shirabe wa shizukesa no youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:23.36,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The melody I dreamed of was like silence.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.23,0:00:28.41,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no te ga mada yume ni tookutemo
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.23,0:00:28.41,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if your hand is still far away in my dreams,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.25,0:00:33.47,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}omoidashiteyou yasashii koe wo
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.25,0:00:33.47,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I’ll still remember your kind voice
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.23,0:00:46.26,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}dareka ga kimi no tame utatta shiawase no koto
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.23,0:00:46.26,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and the happiness that was sung for you.
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.00,0:00:55.66,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}sora no woto hibike takaku kanashimi wo koete
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.00,0:00:55.66,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Let the sound of the sky ring high over your sadness.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.43,0:01:06.21,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no me ni utsuru mono wa subete hontou no sekai
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.43,0:01:06.21,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything reflected in your eyes is that of the real world.
Dialogue: 6,0:01:06.04,0:01:15.68,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}namida sae kimi wo koko ni todomete okenai
Dialogue: 6,0:01:06.04,0:01:15.68,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even tears won’t be able to stop you here.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.41,0:01:27.81,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}furisosogu hikari no naka ashita wo kanadete
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.41,0:01:27.81,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Amidst the descending lights, you’ll play the song of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:47.38,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's remember our love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:47.38,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou omoikasanete
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.59,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}and play out their importance.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.59,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}taisetsu wo kanadeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}We were so happy that we cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:08.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}ureshikute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}It hurt so much that we laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}itakute waratta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:23.71,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}But these are all proof that we are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:23.71,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}dakedo sonna zenbu ga ikiteru akashi nan desu
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.42,0:23:28.05,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's move forward one step at a time.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.42,0:23:28.05,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}yukkuri aruite yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:29.51,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:34.01,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let me hear the words of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:34.01,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}hitosashi no honne kikasete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.22,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.89,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Even if our love and friendship sometimes waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.89,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou toki ni yuretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:41.19,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}I know, you know, a little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:46.82,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}let's make it echo forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:46.82,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}zutto zutto hibiki aitai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:47.19,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:53.16,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.90,0:23:53.16,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}arifureteru kotoba de wa tsutaekirenai
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.86,0:23:58.95,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.86,0:23:58.95,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}watashitachi no harmony
Dialogue: 2,0:23:58.87,0:24:04.00,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear it? Our harmony!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:58.87,0:24:04.00,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}kikoeru our harmony
